#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails aims at providing a \"safe\" environment to produce and optionally "
"publish sensitive documents."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Office suite"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails includes OpenOffice.org, which is a full-featured office productivity "
"suite that provides a near drop-in replacement for Microsoft(R) Office."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "It includes a word processor, a spreadsheet and a presentation application."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "You can launch them from the *Applications* → *Office*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Graphics"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails includes [The GIMP](gimp.org) for The GNU Image Manipulation Program "
"for bitmap graphics. GIMP lets you draw, paint, edit images, and much more."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "For vector-based drawing, Tails includes [inkscape](www.inkscape.org)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Both are accessible from *Applications* → *Graphics* menu."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Audio"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"[Audacity](audacity.sourceforge.net) is a multi-track audio editor for "
"Linux/Unix, MacOS and Windows.  It is designed for easy recording, playing "
"and editing of digital audio."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Desktop publishing"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"[Scribus](scribus.org) is an Open Source Desktop Page Layout accessible from "
"the *Applications* → *Graphics*. It can be used for many tasks; from "
"brochure design to newspapers, magazines, newsletters and posters to "
"technical documentation. It has sophisticated page layout features like "
"precision placing and rotating of text and/or images on a page, manual "
"kerning of type, bezier curves polygons, precision placement of objects, "
"layering with RGB and CMYK custom colors. The Scribus document file format "
"is XML-based. Unlike proprietary binary file formats, even damaged "
"documents, can be recovered with a simple text editor."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Printing and scanning"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The [CUPS printing system](cups.org), which includes drivers for several "
"common printers allows printing, while you can scan with [Simple "
"scan](launchpad.net/simple-scan)"
msgstr ""
